name: Listened to Dear Internet Episode 32 – Waffle House Atlas

content.html:
Dear Internet, I never say this, but this is a good one you all. We finally answer one of the most talked about questions on our twitter. That’s right we are talking all about the guy who fights the cook at waffle house. Also, as a bonus we script the entire Hollywood movie based on this story. Also in this episode, we talk about selling breast milk to body builders and embarrassing audio books. Stay gold, XOXO We are a new show, and would greatly appreciate if you could leave us a 5-star review on your podcast app of choice! If you want more Dear Internet, please consider supporting us on patreon through Dear Internet. Sincerely, The coHosts- Nick Bristow, Jennifer Cheek, Michael DiMauro, and Tim Lanning! Apple Podcast, Spotify, RSS – follow us on Twitter!

By Dear Internet
